Re-use last ujoules setting if current value is invalid

Try to workaround invalid ujoules setting, keeps running average
smoother.

Signed-off-by: Colin Ian King <colin.i.king@gmail.com>

Ignore power readings that are zero

On some kernels on AMD devices it has been observed that power
readings can sometimes drop to zero. Add a check for this and
ignore these samples.

Signed-off-by: Colin Ian King <colin.i.king@gmail.com>
